('ONET-PSYCHIATRIC_AIDES', 'source_onet_psychiatric_aides', 'Psychiatric Aides', 'Psychiatric Aides is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Assist mentally impaired or emotionally disturbed patients, working under direction of nursing and medical staff. May assist with daily living activities, lead patients in educational and recreational activities, or accompany patients to and from examinations and treatments. May restrain violent patients. Includes psychiatric orderlies.', ARRAY['Behavior Aide','Behavior Assistant','Behavior Intervention Assistant','Behavior Support Assistant','Behavioral Aide','Behavioral Assistant','Behavioral Health Assistant','BHA (Behavioral Health Aide)','BHA (Behavioral Health Associate)','Charge Aide','Charge Attendant','Clinical Assistant','Developmental Aide','Direct Care Worker','Health Service Worker','Mental Health Aide (MHA)','Mental Health Assistant','Mental Health Associate','Mental Health Orderly','Mental Health Program Assistant','Mental Health Worker (MHW)','Neuropsychiatric Aide','Psychiatric Aide','Psychiatric Assistant','Psychiatric Attendant','Psychiatric Nursing Aide','Psychiatric Orderly','Psychiatric Technician Assistant (Psychiatric Tech Assistant)','Qualified Medication Aide (QMA)','Resident Care Technician (Resident Care Tech)','Residential Care Tech (Residential Care Technician)','Therapeutic Program Worker (TPW)']::text[], ARRAY['Psychiatric Aides','Behavior Aide','Behavior Assistant','Behavior Intervention Assistant','Behavior Support Assistant','Behavioral Aide','Behavioral Assistant','Behavioral Health Assistant','BHA (Behavioral Health Aide)','BHA (Behavioral Health Associate)','Charge Aide','Charge Attendant','Clinical Assistant','Developmental Aide','Direct Care Worker','Health Service Worker','Mental Health Aide (MHA)','Mental Health Assistant','Mental Health Associate','Mental Health Orderly','Mental Health Program Assistant','